{"tid":2443561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本奧運大臣︰日本運動員不合資格接種中國疫苗","createTime":"2021-03-12T06:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T17:23:07.000Z","uid":39464,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1c9e0838e76fb8bf610b542d0043e2f11b330f3d","tid":2443561,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:36:39.000Z","msg":"中國提出向參加7月東京奧運會和明年北京冬奧的運動員及代表團提供新冠疫苗，國際奧委會將會支付額外的疫苗費用。日本奧運大臣丸川珠代說，由於中國疫苗未有在日本獲批准使用，因此日本代表隊的成員不符合接種資格。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2382709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2382709&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=599747e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2382709</a>"},{"pid":"f451002d32c4ec70c824aa6daceda5046ac5c309","tid":2443561,"uid":364850,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:37:54.000Z","msg":"國際奧委會將會支付額外的疫苗費用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de278ecb816001144f4a3da80e0d3701a597125c","tid":2443561,"uid":22624,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:46:27.000Z","msg":"支持，日本人冇資格打中國疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23bfd10194f79c8360c233ff6ee0385f75348e73","tid":2443561,"uid":55913,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T06:46:42.000Z","msg":"打死晒外國d運動員咪贏到冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0192ea85a575dad6ace78ddbf